page.title: 15Interesting People
page.content: Anna and Vanessa Murby are twins who are aged 14 years. They both attend Campion School Bugbrooke and are both interested in Music. They live in Kislingbury so they go to school by bus Both girls are in the County Youth Orchestra, at the Music School. They rehearse every Saturday. The rehearsal fills the whole morning. After this they go to another music group "Conducting Classes" followed closely by a twentieth century music group. Most Saturday Evenings the twins go to a Concert or are in a Concert. Many of these are at the Derngate Northampton. The musical instruments they are interested in are : Piano Clarinet Viola
